<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 06:10:52 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>人民币汇率触及三个月低点后触及三周以来最低水平</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/chinas-yuan-hits-weakest-level-in-3-weeks-after-fix-set-at-3-month-low/articleshow/110289396.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110289396.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于央行下调指导利率以打击资本外流，人民币兑美元走弱。周二，人民币兑美元汇率跌至三周低点。马银行分析师将人民币贬值与资本外流恶化以及对住房救助计划资金的担忧联系起来。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 04:23:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/chinas-yuan-hits-weakest-level-in-3-weeks-after-fix-set-at-3-month-low/articleshow/110289396.cms</guid></item><item><title>重要会议召开，巴黎争夺欧洲人工智能桂冠</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/paris-vies-for-europes-ai-crown-as-key-conference-beckons/articleshow/110290735.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110290735.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;法国在 Viva Technology 举办技术领袖峰会，希望巩固巴黎作为人工智能中心的地位。 LVMH 旗下的 Arnault 展示奢侈品牌。马克龙利用巴黎的奢华地位吸引了对生成型人工智能初创公司的投资。亚马逊和微软在法国科技领域进行投资，努力整合资本市场并吸引科技投资。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 05:09:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/paris-vies-for-europes-ai-crown-as-key-conference-beckons/articleshow/110290735.cms</guid></item><item><title>新加坡在马来西亚警察局袭击后加强安全</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/singapore-boosts-security-after-malaysia-police-station-attack/articleshow/110291242.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110291242.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;新加坡总理黄循财周二表示，一名涉嫌与基地组织有联系的男子袭击了邻国马来西亚的一个警察局，新加坡加强了安全措施。新加坡新当选总理黄说：“这样的袭击发生在我们的边界之外，无情地提醒我们恐怖主义的威胁仍然很高。”</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 05:25:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/singapore-boosts-security-after-malaysia-police-station-attack/articleshow/110291242.cms</guid></item><item><title>周二的初选包括总统竞选和特朗普佐治亚州选举案中的检察官</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/tuesdays-primaries-include-presidential-races-and-the-prosecutor-in-trumps-georgia-election-case/articleshow/110290234.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110290234.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乔·拜登和唐纳德·特朗普的总统初选即将结束，随着肯塔基州和俄勒冈州即将做出的象征性决定，他们面临着异议。影响全国代表大会、代表，并揭示民主党和共和党基础的情绪。各种州初选和关键竞选在多个州展开，包括佐治亚州、加利福尼亚州和俄勒冈州，在区和县级别都有重要的比赛。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 04:50:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/tuesdays-primaries-include-presidential-races-and-the-prosecutor-in-trumps-georgia-election-case/articleshow/110290234.cms</guid></item><item><title>所罗门群岛告诉澳大利亚它仍然是首选合作伙伴</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/solomon-islands-tells-australia-it-remains-partner-of-choice/articleshow/110289947.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110289947.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;新当选的所罗门群岛总理马内莱寻求扩大与澳大利亚的合作，以应对中国在该地区的影响。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 04:41:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/solomon-islands-tells-australia-it-remains-partner-of-choice/articleshow/110289947.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国因用受污染的血液感染数千人并掩盖丑闻而受到调查</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/britain-slammed-in-inquiry-for-infecting-thousands-with-tainted-blood-and-covering-up-the-scandal/articleshow/110288861.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110288861.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一项调查揭露英国当局通过受污染的血液使患者遭受致命感染，导致死亡和终身疾病。前法官布赖恩·兰斯塔夫批评了国家医疗服务体系，并强调了艾滋病毒感染的影响。报告还提到使用高危捐献者的血浆以及通过输血传播丙型肝炎。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 04:02:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/britain-slammed-in-inquiry-for-infecting-thousands-with-tainted-blood-and-covering-up-the-scandal/articleshow/110288861.cms</guid></item><item><title>澳元、新西兰元已经耗尽，思考利率前景</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/australia-nz-dollars-run-out-of-puff-ponder-rate-outlooks/articleshow/110288780.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110288780.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于市场评估利率稳定，澳元和新西兰元走弱。铜价飙升至历史新高，支撑主要大宗商品。澳洲联储发布会议纪要，暗示可能加息，等待通胀和消费者数据。新西兰联储预计将维持官方现金利率不变，市场预计八月份可能会降息。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 04:00:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/australia-nz-dollars-run-out-of-puff-ponder-rate-outlooks/articleshow/110288780.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列和哈马斯拒绝国际刑事法院以战争罪逮捕领导人的请求</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-hamas-reject-bid-before-icc-to-arrest-leaders-for-war-crimes/articleshow/110288757.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110288757.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列和哈马斯在美国的反对下拒绝了国际刑事法院检察官卡里姆·汗在加沙地带逮捕战争罪领导人的请求，南非对国际刑事法院的举动表示欢迎，而法国则表示支持法院的独立性“以及反对恐怖主义的斗争”。在所有情况下都不受惩罚&amp;quot;。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 03:58:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-hamas-reject-bid-before-icc-to-arrest-leaders-for-war-crimes/articleshow/110288757.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普在真相社交视频中发表“统一帝国”的帖子引发愤怒</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-sparks-outrage-with-unified-reich-post-in-truth-social-video/articleshow/110288852.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110288852.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 04:02:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-sparks-outrage-with-unified-reich-post-in-truth-social-video/articleshow/110288852.cms</guid></item><item><title>谷物-小麦从近期涨势中回落，但全球供应困境限制了损失</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/grains-wheat-retreats-from-recent-rally-but-global-supply-woes-limit-losses/articleshow/110287885.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110287885.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于美国冬季作物评级下降和俄罗斯霜冻损害，芝加哥小麦期货在上涨近 6% 后回落。大豆和玉米价格也下跌，而美国农业部报告了作物状况。澳大利亚农作物面临干燥天气的威胁，乌克兰北部和东部的严重霜冻也可能减少谷物和油籽收成。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 03:27:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/grains-wheat-retreats-from-recent-rally-but-global-supply-woes-limit-losses/articleshow/110287885.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗西北部为已故总统举行葬礼</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/funerary-procession-to-be-held-for-late-president-in-irans-northwest/articleshow/110288169.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110288169.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 03:42:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/funerary-procession-to-be-held-for-late-president-in-irans-northwest/articleshow/110288169.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦：伊沙克·达尔敦促对比什凯克暴徒袭击事件的肇事者迅速采取行动</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-ishaq-dar-urges-swift-action-against-perpetrators-of-bishkek-mob-attacks/articleshow/110287628.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110287628.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;副总理穆罕默德·伊沙克·达尔在阿斯塔纳敦促吉尔吉斯斯坦外交部长热恩贝克·库卢巴耶夫解决暴徒袭击外国学生的问题，其中包括比什凯克的巴基斯坦学生。讨论内容包括吉尔吉斯斯坦的巴基斯坦学生的担忧、确保他们的安全以及吉尔吉斯政府恢复法律和秩序的行动。吉尔吉斯斯坦政府保证为巴基斯坦学生安全遣返提供安全保障和便利。吉尔吉斯斯坦内务部发布新闻稿称，局势已得到控制。没有死亡报告。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 03:18:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-ishaq-dar-urges-swift-action-against-perpetrators-of-bishkek-mob-attacks/articleshow/110287628.cms</guid></item><item><title>耶鲁大学毕业生在毕业典礼上举行支持巴勒斯坦的罢工</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/yale-graduates-stage-pro-palestinian-walkout-of-commencement/articleshow/110286808.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110286808.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;耶鲁大学的学生走出毕业典礼，抗议以色列在加沙的战争、耶鲁大学与武器制造商的关系以及对亲巴勒斯坦示威活动的回应。至少 150 名坐在观众席前部的学生一起站起来，背对舞台，穿过菲尔普斯门走出仪式，沿着游行队伍的脚步回到院子里。许多抗议者举着小横幅，上面写着“书籍不要炸弹”和“远离战争”等口号。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 02:45:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/yale-graduates-stage-pro-palestinian-walkout-of-commencement/articleshow/110286808.cms</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚和新西兰派遣航班前往新喀里多尼亚</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/australia-new-zealand-send-evacuation-flights-to-new-caledonia/articleshow/110286554.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110286554.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;澳大利亚和新西兰周二表示，他们将派遣政府飞机从新喀里多尼亚撤离国民，新喀里多尼亚一直面临法国政府带来的选举变化引发的致命骚乱。这些骚乱甚至导致商业航班取消。截至目前，已有六人死亡。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 02:26:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/australia-new-zealand-send-evacuation-flights-to-new-caledonia/articleshow/110286554.cms</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚因输电线路延误而面临停电风险</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/australia-runs-risk-of-blackouts-amid-transmission-lines-delay/articleshow/110286775.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110286775.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于风能和太阳能发电厂输电线路安装延误，澳大利亚面临电力短缺，影响了该国的能源转型计划。这是到 2030 年实现可再生能源电力目标的一项挑战，而扩大输电网络以处理远离需求中心的新可再生能源项目正在阻碍进展。项目开发和调试的延迟以及对备用电源的需求正在增加可靠性风险。为了避免供应短缺，需要新建和升级约10,000公里的输电线路。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 02:42:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/australia-runs-risk-of-blackouts-amid-transmission-lines-delay/articleshow/110286775.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国因腐败对前孟加拉国将军实施制裁</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-imposes-sanctions-on-former-bangladeshi-general-over-corruption/articleshow/110286553.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110286553.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 02:26:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-imposes-sanctions-on-former-bangladeshi-general-over-corruption/articleshow/110286553.cms</guid></item><item><title>证人警告说，法官清场后，特朗普的审判变得混乱</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-hush-money-trial-michael-cohen-stormy-daniels/articleshow/110286253.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110286253.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在周一的证词中，迈克尔·科恩承认通过夸大封口费报销费用，从唐纳德·特朗普那里窃取了 3 万美元。在盘问的第四天，科恩被问及他向斯托米·丹尼尔斯支付的 13 万美元所收到的较大还款中的很大一部分。科恩声称，这笔还款包括额外支付给 Red Finch 的 5 万美元，Red Finch 是一家受雇来提高特朗普在 CNBC 选前民意调查中排名的科技公司。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 02:16:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-hush-money-trial-michael-cohen-stormy-daniels/articleshow/110286253.cms</guid></item><item><title>“我们拒绝这一点”：拜登称以色列对加沙的进攻不是种族灭绝</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/we-reject-that-biden-says-israels-gaza-offensive-not-genocide/articleshow/110282191.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110282191.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;他说：“正在发生的事情不是种族灭绝，我们拒绝承认这一点。”他指的是位于海牙的联合国最高法院国际法院的一个案件，该案件声称以色列的战争是种族灭绝。拜登还重申谴责国际刑事法院检察官周一提出的对以色列领导人发出逮捕令的请求。国际刑事法院是一个独立的法庭。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 22:16:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/we-reject-that-biden-says-israels-gaza-offensive-not-genocide/articleshow/110282191.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯吞并的卢甘斯克负责人表示，乌克兰炮击损坏了燃料库</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/head-of-russia-annexed-luhansk-says-ukrainian-shelling-damages-fuel-depot/articleshow/110281708.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110281708.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 20:32:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/head-of-russia-annexed-luhansk-says-ukrainian-shelling-damages-fuel-depot/articleshow/110281708.cms</guid></item><item><title>那些哑剧在监视我们吗？在巴基斯坦，这不是一个奇怪的问题</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/are-those-mimes-spying-on-us-in-pakistan-its-not-a-strange-question/articleshow/110281673.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/110281673.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在这种氛围下，每个人——甚至街头艺人——都可以被视为国家的潜在工具。在巴基斯坦 76 年历史的大部分时间里，监视是日常生活的常态。但近年来，人们对军队在政治中的作用感到不满。 25 岁的伊斯兰堡居民阿里·阿巴斯 (Ali Abas) 表示：“由于政治气氛如此两极分化，我们越来越怀疑是否有人在监视或在倾听。”</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 20:13:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/are-those-mimes-spying-on-us-in-pakistan-its-not-a-strange-question/articleshow/110281673.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>